,('b0a5f161-7ec8-4d20-ba88-2db7fe140ca6','<p>As a solution architect, you contribute to the digital transformation of the bank and are the driving force behind developments, such as Open Banking. All development is done within the cloud using the latest cutting-edge technology.</p>
