<p>It is up to the squad to manage who takes part in discussions with users and stakeholders to come to concrete new features of your product.<br>Sometimes users experience difficulties while integrating your product with their own solution. In such situations, your squad helps the user to tackle these issues. All squad members take part in this technical support towards users.<br><br>Responsibilities</p>
