</ul>
<p><br><b>What you will be doing</b></p>
<ul>
 <li>Work with Product Owner to understand and refine functional specifications and how they translate in application features.</li>
 <li>Use Calypso, Java and other supporting tools to build the requested features.</li>
 <li>Work on strategic projects and coordinate with other IT teams and you are able to take a leading role.</li>
