,('99052f60-2360-4b11-9270-f3a8f01ae365','<p>Are you passionate about cyber security, big data and artificial intelligence? Are you up for the challenge to drive an initiative through our innovation framework? If this triggers your attention, you are in the right place. At the ING Labs, we are working on a new initiative that will combine these domains into cutting edge solutions.</p>
<p><b>Your work environment</b></p>
<p>ING’s purpose is to empower people in life and in business by increasing the pace of innovation to serve changing customer needs. ING Labs focus on thinking beyond traditional banking to develop new services to take to market. This specific initiative will focus on <b>Cyber Security, AI and Big Data.</b></p>
<p>You will be working in the ING Labs Amsterdam office in a very international and dynamic environment. Using ING’s customer led innovation process you will validate the key assumptions of the Cybersecurity proposition and business. </p>
<p><b>A market to develop</b></p>
<p>ING Labs funds disruptive ventures addressing multi-billion Euro market opportunities. Our initiative will support these ventures like Cobase and Yolt with a design process aimed at de-risking before going to market (using lean startup, design thinking &amp; agile methodologies). </p>
<p><b>Your role</b></p>
<p>As a Senior Software Engineer, you will be the expert in your domain area and a key member of the team to support us in a new initiative starting from scratch.</p>
<p>You are passionate and at your best working to solve very hard problems with a small highly skilled team. You want to work in a startup with the backing of a large innovative bank. Your curiosity and vision drive you to build what has never been built before. </p>
<p><b>Your deliverables</b></p>
<p>In the next 6 months, we are expected to bring this initiative to the next level and demonstrate a compelling story to ING’s innovation fund. Along the way, key assumptions will be validated with the goal of creating a new start-up and later scale-up, inside or outside of ING. Delivery is key so as a seasoned engineer, your ability rapidly develop and deploy new software will help us achieve this short term goal; only the beginning of our ambitious journey.</p>
<p><b>Your profile</b></p>
<p>Technical skills required:</p>
<ul>
 <li>Experienced in java development. You can hit the ground running and do not need training</li>
 <li>JVM internals knowledge</li>
 <li>Experienced in implementing AI algorithms</li>
 <li>Good understanding of compilers (e.g lexical analysis)</li>
 <li>Basic Python</li>
 <li>Acquainted best practices in secure coding</li>
</ul>
<p>Others:</p>
