<p>We need all our team players to be familiar with Scrum and DevOps processes as well as software engineering and design principles, clean code, TDD/BDD and a few common tools like Confluence, Docker, Git, GitLab, Jira, Maven, and Miro. Because we''re working internationally teamwork and fluent English are a must, other languages are a bonus!&nbsp;</p>
