,('78c474ad-1ecd-4d81-a628-5a94ec6c7b74','<p><b>Your position</b></p>
<p>As IT Process Consultant&nbsp;in the development of Software Deployment services, you design and implement an IT Operations framework of the following ITIL processes (incl R&amp;R / Organization):</p>
<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Validation and Testing</p>
<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Release and Deployment</p>
<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;CI/CD pipeline integration</p>
<p>For an increasing number of customers our client is delivering continuous software updates to the products and the systems with our customers. </p>
