<p> Life-cycle Services accounts for more than 20% of the total sales at our client. The Global Services department is responsible for centrally organized services – like Service Desk and Spare parts – and for the development and improvement of new services. The IT Service Development team is one of the expert teams and is responsible for our client''s IT Services strategy. The team works closely together with other expert teams (e.g. asset management services, logistic services, data driven services) and in close cooperation with the Customer Centers to define and realize our client''s Life-cycle Services strategy.&nbsp;</p>
